  "description": "Do you want to explore the tallest dungeon tower ever? You've found the right mod!",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E9hENAd.png\" alt=\"banner1\"></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/sdob\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/refs/heads/v3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_64h.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"> </a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/sdob\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/refs/heads/v3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_64h.png\" alt=\"CurseForge\"> </a><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/C8W2duu.png\" alt=\"datapack\"> <a href=\"https://gamejolt.com/games/sdob/953274\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h85Hg1b.png\" alt=\"GameJolt\"> </a><a href=\"https://d4vide106.itch.io/sdob-mc\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qz2uWJJ.png\" alt=\"Itch.io\"></a></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>🗼 Spiral Dungeon of Babel 🗼</strong><br>Inspired by the <em>DanMachi</em> series, this mod brings a fully vanilla-style, towering structure over 300 blocks tall with 30 challenging levels. Rare to find and packed with epic adventures, it’s a test of courage for the boldest adventurers!</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><span><span><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"340\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8fnO7HA9wRY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></span></span></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><h3>🌟 The First Floors of the Spiral Dungeon of Babel 🌟</h3><ul><li>🟤 <strong>1st Floor: The Forge of Hephaestus</strong> – Home to the god of craftsmanship, filled with tools and secrets.</li><li>🌌 <strong>2nd Floor: Nyx's Realm</strong> – Shrouded in darkness, where shadows come to life.</li><li>🌿 <strong>3rd Floor: Demeter's Garden</strong> – A lush haven guarded by nature’s wrath.</li></ul></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>📢 Have feedback or found a bug?</strong><br><a href=\"https://discord.gg/thfPJ7QAPJ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/refs/heads/v3/assets/compact/social/discord-plural_46h.png\" alt=\"Discord\"></a></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><strong>💖 Support by donating!</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/checkout/InfinityWonderful?rid=0&amp;cadence=1&amp;custom=1\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/refs/heads/v3/assets/compact/donate/patreon-singular_46h.png\" alt=\"Patreon\"></a><br><em>Your support helps me improve and update the mod. Thank you!</em></div>\n\n* * *\n\n<div style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>🌟 Mod Usage</strong><br>Feel free to include <strong>Spiral Dungeon of Babel</strong> in modpacks or share it, ensuring proper credit to D4vide106 and linking to the official sources (Modrinth, CurseForge, etc.).</div>",
